Package: stressPLS
Title: Stress-Test Formative Higher-Order Constructs in PLS-SEM
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("stressPLS", "contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "stresspls@example.com")
Author: stressPLS contributors
Maintainer: stressPLS contributors <stresspls@example.com>
Description: Provides an initial framework for generating and reporting
    stress-test perturbation grids for formative higher-order constructs in
    partial least squares structural equation models. The package is designed
    around modular model specifications, perturbation generation, estimation
    backends, robustness scoring, and reporting.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://stresspls.github.io/stressPLS/
